abstract: >-
  Codex 13 Student Dev Kit is a Windows installer that sets up a portable
  development environment toolkit for students, classrooms, workshops and
  project-based learning in a user-selected folder without requiring
  administrator rights. It supports bilingual installation (Polish and English),
  multiple profiles (Start, Classroom), and portable installs of VS Code, Git
  for Windows, and XAMPP.
